01:16:31.285 --> 01:16:34.168
u upaljače, šnale kaiša.

01:16:34.360 --> 01:16:35.691
To je olovka.

01:16:35.800 --> 01:16:37.484
Alatka za pisanje.

01:16:38.000 --> 01:16:39.554
Je li?

01:16:46.760 --> 01:16:48.293
Šta je to?

01:16:48.920 --> 01:16:50.490
Čaura utrošenog metka.

01:16:50.600 --> 01:16:54.525
To je, g. Marlou, pištolj.

01:16:54.640 --> 01:16:56.642
To je...

01:16:56.760 --> 01:17:00.273
olovka-pištolj kalibra 22.

01:17:00.313 --> 01:17:01.774
Pogledaj tačno ovde.

01:17:01.814 --> 01:17:03.481
To je ranilo Koblinskog.

01:17:03.600 --> 01:17:05.045
